- Levels are problems to solve

- Rats in an asteroid
- Ghost ship in a foggy nebula

Q: What
A: Anarchist space gardening rats that live in a mined-out asteroid.
Being raided by bad guys.

Q: Why
A: To steal the rare plant species

Q: Technology Level
A: Medium. Has large water lake for the plants that feeds into the hydroponic levels.
Has a large dining area and burrows.

Raiders have mobile turrets and have overrided some doors.

# Units

1 unit = 1 meter
protagonist height = 1.75m
protagonist diameter = 0.5m
